---

##  Quick Notes / Key Takeaways
- SOC work is **teamwork** — no analyst handles everything alone.  
- Communication is as critical as technical analysis.  
- The basic workflow: **Alert → Triage → Escalation → Response.**  
- Blocking an IP is just the start — always investigate the root cause.  

